<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.8">
<l>ūḻiyā yōmat tucciyā yorukā luṭaiyatē roruvaṉā yulakil</l>
<l>cūḻimāl yāṉait tuyarkeṭut tilaṅkai malaṅkavaṉ ṟaṭucaran turantu</l>
<l>pāḻiyāl mikka pārttaṉuk karuḷip pakalava ṉoḷikeṭap pakalē</l>
<l>yāḻiyā laṉṟaṅ kāḻiyai maṟaittā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam, becoming the ages,</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming the zenith of the sacrifice,</l>
<l>Becoming the one with the one-wheeled chariot, having ended the suffering</l>
<l rend="indent">in [this] world of the dark caparisoned elephant,</l>
<l>Having shot a burning arrow that day to torment Lanka,</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one who, granting grace to Pārtha</l>
<l rend="indent">whose strength was truly great,</l>
<l>So the light of the day-maker was ruined,</l>
<l rend="indent">then and there at daytime, hid the sun with his discus.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
